title: Adrian and Raz Best Of Vocal Trance (2014) (320kbps) (AciDToX8)

Adrian and Raz Best Of Vocal Trance (2014) 

                              Trance | Adrian & Raz

            320 kbps | MP3 | unmixed | 2014-01-13 | 01:18:32 | 184 Mb


The last years have seen our labels receiving so much support by so many great DJ's like Armin, Axwell, Markus, Ferry, Above & Beyond and many many more. We're counting our blessings for working with all these incredible talents like Ana Criado, Beat Service, Neev Kennedy, Two&One, DJ Feel, Jan Johnston, Sarah Russell, Katty Heath. This compilation is a celebration of all our talented artists, their songs and their biggest records. Included are the block busters "Obsession" (Yuri Kane feat. Sopheary), Higher (Rafael Frost & Jennifer Rene), "Whispers" (Ana Criado & Beat Service), "Open Your Eyes" (Aurosonic feat. Kate Louise Smith), "Lonely People 2014" (Team Bastian vs. Two&One feat. Sir Adrian), Never Coming Down (Invalyd feat. Polina) and many many more Trancefloor killers. Enjoy! WWW | http://adrianrazrecordings.com FACEBOOK |TWITTER |YOUTUBE |
